OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome fine
OL,6,Fevening sunshine, but cloud building
OL,7,Ffrom the west overnight. Outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain arriving in the north and west by
OL,9,Fmorning, turning heavy at times. A
OL,10,Fmild night for most.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy with rain in the north
OL,13,Fat first. Cloud tending to break up a
OL,14,Flittle allowing frequent showers to
OL,15,Fdevelop, some heavy with thunder
OL,16,Fpossible, but dry spells too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
