OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry with sunny spells, but some rain
OL,7,Fpossible at times towards the
OL,8,Fnorthwest, especially overnight into
OL,9,FThursday. Temperatures near average
OL,10,Fbut slowly edging up.
